# AeroLIT PXE Content: Profiles, Overrides, and Emergency Edits

This document explains how PXE profiles work, how to add or override profiles, how to override Kickstart templates, and how emergency edits under `/ks` behave.

## Where the files live

Current project layout used by the image:

```text
content/
  profiles/
    10-developer-workstation.yml
    20-security-baseline.yml
    30-security-luks.yml
    40-embedded-edge.yml
    50-minimal.yml
    60-small-disk.yml
  examples/overrides/
    profiles/
      10-minimal-override.example.yml
    templates/ks/
      rhel8-minimal.example.ks.j2
  ui/
    background.png
scripts/
